#. Tag: title
#: search.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "KruSearcher: find what you are looking for"
msgstr "KruSearcher: poiščite, kar iščete"

#. Tag: primary
#: search.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search"
msgstr "Iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Welcome to &krusader;'s powerful search module - nicknamed KruSearcher. It "
"is the most able tool (that we know of) for &Linux;, since it allows so many "
"different ways to quickly find the file you are looking for. The search "
"function is also available on remote file systems. It is divided into two "
"levels, the general and the advanced. Let's take a look at the general page."
msgstr ""
"Dobrodošli v zmogljivem iskalnem modulu &krusader; z vzdevkom KruSearcher. "
"Je najzmogljivejše orodje (kar jih poznamo) za &Linux;, saj omogoča toliko "
"različnih načinov za hitro iskanje datoteke, ki jo iščete. Funkcija iskanja "
"je na voljo tudi v oddaljenih datotečnih sistemih. Razdeljen je na dve "
"ravni, splošno in napredno. Oglejmo si splošno stran."

#. Tag: title
#: search.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General Search</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošno iskanje</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: search.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>General Search</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošno iskanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The page is divided into four parts: top (search for) part, bottom part - "
"titled <guilabel>Containing text</guilabel>, left part - titled "
"<guilabel>Search in</guilabel> and right part which is called <guilabel>Do "
"not search in</guilabel>. Obviously, each part handles different aspects of "
"the search. Let's look at them closely."
msgstr ""
"Stran je razdeljena na štiri dele: zgornji (iskanje) del, spodnji del z "
"naslovom <guilabel>Vsebuje besedilo</guilabel>, levi del z naslovom "
"<guilabel>Išči v</guilabel> in desni del z imenom <guilabel >Ne išči v</"
"guilabel>. Očitno vsak del obravnava različne vidike iskanja. Oglejmo si jih "
"natančno."

#. Tag: title
#: search.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Top Part:"
msgstr "Zgornji del:"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Search for</guilabel>: here you enter the main search criteria. "
"You can enter a file name, a wildcard ( <literal role=\"extension\">*.o.*</"
"literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">*.c</literal> &etc;) or both - "
"separated by a space. If you type <literal>'text'</literal> the results is "
"the same as <literal>'*text*'</literal>. You can exclude files from the "
"search with '|' (&eg; <literal role=\"extension\">'*.cpp *.h | *.moc.cpp'</"
"literal>). You can use quotation marks for names that contain spaces. Filter "
"<quote>Program Files</quote> searches out those files/folders the name of "
"which is <filename>Program Files</filename>. A drop-down list that is shown "
"after clicking down arrow on the right allows you to pick some of your "
"previously entered criteria."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Išči</guilabel>: tukaj vnesete glavne iskalne kriterije. Vnesete "
"lahko ime datoteke, nadomestni znak ( <literal role=\"extension\">*.o.*</"
"literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">*.c</literal> &etc;) ali oboje – "
"ločeno s presledkom. Če vnesete <literal>'text'</literal>, so rezultati "
"enaki kot <literal>'*text*'</literal>. Datoteke lahko izključite iz iskanja "
"z '|' (&eg; <literal role=\"extension\">'*.cpp *.h | *.moc.cpp'</literal>). "
"Za imena, ki vsebujejo presledke, lahko uporabite narekovaje. Filter "
"<quote>Programske datoteke</quote> išče tiste datoteke/mape, katerih ime je "
"<filename>Programske datoteke</filename>. Spustni seznam, ki se prikaže po "
"kliku puščice navzdol na desni, vam omogoča, da izberete nekaj svojih "
"predhodno vnesenih kriterijev."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to edit the list of suggestions for the <guilabel>Search for</"
"guilabel> field. If you do not like some of its items just select it and "
"press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> and "
"that useless suggestion gets deleted. You can also use the arrow keys in "
"order to see all the history in the <guilabel>Search for</guilabel> field, "
"and delete the entries that are needless."
msgstr ""
"Možno je urediti seznam predlogov za polje <guilabel>Išči</guilabel>. Če vam "
"nekateri predmeti niso všeč, jih preprosto izberite in pritisnite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> in ta neuporaben "
"predlog bo izbrisan. Uporabite lahko tudi puščične tipke, da si ogledate vso "
"zgodovino v polju <guilabel>Išči</guilabel> in izbrišete vnose, ki niso "
"potrebni."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case sensitive</guilabel>: unchecking it will allow lower and "
"upper case search (&ie;: <literal role=\"extension\">*.c</literal> "
"interprets as <literal role=\"extension\">*.c</literal> AND <literal role="
"\"extension\">*.C</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami</guilabel>: če počistite "
"polje, boste omogočili iskanje z malimi in velikimi črkami (&ie;: <literal "
"role=\"extension\">*.c</literal> razlaga kot <literal role=\"extension\">*. "
"c</literal> IN <literal role=\"extension\">*.C</literal>)."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Of type</guilabel>: this box lets you search for a file not only "
"by its name, but also by its &MIME; type. For example, you can search for "
"all the audio files whose name begins with B. Usually this option defaults "
"to 'all files', but you can choose to search for archives, folders, images, "
"text files, videos and audio files."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vrsta</guilabel>: to polje vam omogoča iskanje datoteke ne samo po "
"imenu, temveč tudi po &MIME; vrsta. Iščete lahko na primer po vseh zvočnih "
"datotekah, katerih ime se začne z B. Običajno je ta možnost privzeto "
"nastavljena na 'vse datoteke', vendar lahko izberete iskanje po arhivih, "
"mapah, slikah, besedilnih datotekah, videoposnetkih in zvočnih datotekah."

#. Tag: title
#: search.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left and Right Part:"
msgstr "Levi in desni del:"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Search in</guilabel> and <guilabel>Do not search in</guilabel>: "
"Using those two parts, you can specify a search exactly the way you want it. "
"For example, you might want to search for a file in the whole file system "
"(beginning with <filename>/</filename>), but do not want to search inside "
"<filename>/mnt</filename>. All you need to do is write <filename>/</"
"filename> in the <guilabel>Search in</guilabel> box, and write <filename>/"
"mnt</filename> in the <guilabel>Do not search in</guilabel> box. If you want "
"to enter more than one folder in one of the list boxes, just type the first "
"name and press &Enter;. The folder name will be copied to the bigger list "
"box and you will be able to enter another name."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Išči v</guilabel> in <guilabel>Ne išči v</guilabel>: Z uporabo teh "
"dveh delov lahko določite iskanje natanko tako, kot želite. Na primer, morda "
"želite iskati datoteko v celotnem datotečnem sistemu (začenši z <filename>/</"
"filename>), vendar ne želite iskati znotraj <filename>/mnt</filename>. Vse "
"kar morate storiti je, da napišete <filename>/</filename> v polje "
"<guilabel>Išči v</guilabel> in vpišete <filename>/mnt</filename> v polje "
"<guilabel>Ne išči v</guilabel>. Če želite v eno od seznamskih polj vnesti "
"več kot eno mapo, samo vnesite ime in pritisnite &Enter;. Ime mape bo "
"kopirano v večje seznamsko polje in lahko boste vnesli drugo ime."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The input line has an auto-completion feature, corresponding to &plasma; "
"global settings. If you wish, you can click on the <guiicon>folder icon</"
"guiicon>, and browse to the folder you wish to add."
msgstr ""
"Vnosna vrstica ima funkcijo samodokončanja, ki ustreza &plasma; globalne "
"nastavitve. Če želite, lahko kliknete <guiicon>ikono mape</guiicon> in "
"poiščete mapo, ki jo želite dodati."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define files and folders which will be filtered out from "
"the search results using the <guilabel>Exclude Folder Names</guilabel> input "
"field at the bottom of the <guilabel>Do not search in</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"Z vnosnim poljem <guilabel>Izključi imena map</guilabel> na dnu polja "
"<guilabel>Ne išči v</guilabel> lahko določite datoteke in mape, ki bodo "
"izločene iz rezultatov iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Items in the filtering list should be space-separated."
msgstr "Elementi na seznamu za filtriranje morajo biti ločeni s presledki."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Spaces in the filtering list items can be escaped or quoted. Example: "
"<userinput>.git \"target build\" build\\ krusader</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Presledke v elementih seznama za filtriranje je mogoče ubežati ali "
"narekovati. Primer: <userinput>.git \"target build\" build\\ krusader</"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: search.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bottom Part:"
msgstr "Spodnji del:"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Text</guilabel>: entering text here makes &krusader; search for it "
"inside the files ( <command>grep</command>). This way you can search for all "
"header files ( <literal role=\"extension\">*.h</literal>) which include the "
"word <literal>'testing 123'</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Besedilo</guilabel>: če tukaj vnesete besedilo, &krusader; "
"poiščite ga znotraj datotek ( <command>grep</command>). Na ta način lahko "
"iščete vse datoteke glave ( <literal role=\"extension\">*.h</literal>), ki "
"vključujejo besedo <literal>'testiranje 123'</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>RegExp</guilabel> switch: toggle the regular expressions mode. A "
"drop-down list that is shown after clicking down arrow on the right allows "
"you to enter special symbols of regular expressions."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>RegExp</guilabel> stikalo: preklopi način regularnih izrazov. "
"Spustni seznam, ki se prikaže po kliku puščice navzdol na desni, vam omogoča "
"vnos posebnih simbolov regularnih izrazov."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Encoding</guilabel>: allows you to choose the text encoding."
msgstr "<guilabel>Kodiranje</guilabel>: omogoča izbiro kodiranja besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Match whole word only</guilabel>: allows you to specify that a "
"complete match (letters and length) must be found."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ujemi samo celotno besedo</guilabel>: omogoča vam, da določite, da "
"je treba najti popolno ujemanje (črke in dolžina)."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case sensitive</guilabel>: refers to your text being searched for "
"in upper and lower case or the exact phrase you entered."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razlikuj med velikimi in malimi črkami</guilabel>: nanaša se na "
"vaše besedilo, ki ga iščete z velikimi in malimi črkami ali točno besedo, ki "
"ste jo vnesli."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Search in sub folders</guilabel>: perform a recursive search and "
"dive into every folder on the way."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Iskanje v podmapah</guilabel>: izvedite rekurzivno iskanje in se "
"potopite v vsako mapo na poti."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Search in archives</guilabel>: &krusader; will search for your "
"files inside every supported archive. This, however, takes longer to perform."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Iskanje v arhivih</guilabel>: &krusader; bo poiskal vaše datoteke "
"znotraj vsakega podprtega arhiva. To pa traja dlje časa."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check this checkbox, you will notice you cannot <command>grep</"
"command> inside files anymore. This is done, since looking inside archived "
"files forces &krusader; to extract them, which results in an extremely time-"
"consuming search."
msgstr ""
"Če označite to potrditveno polje, boste opazili, da ne morete več "
"<command>grep</command> znotraj datotek. To je storjeno, saj pogled v "
"arhivirane datoteke prisili &krusader; jih izluščiti, kar ima za posledico "
"izjemno zamudno iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Follow links</guilabel>: if checked, &krusader; will follow soft-"
"links during the search."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sledi povezavam</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; bo med "
"iskanjem sledil mehkim povezavam."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Profiles</guilabel>: if you have to regularly perform the same "
"search operation, you can save the search settings &eg; include files, "
"exclude files, &etc;... Press the 'profile' button, and you can add/load/"
"save/remove search profiles."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Profili</guilabel>: če morate redno izvajati isto operacijo "
"iskanja, lahko shranite nastavitve iskanja &eg; vključi datoteke, izključi "
"datoteke &etc;.... Pritisnite gumb 'profil' in lahko dodate/naložite/"
"shranite/odstranite iskalne profile."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Query to clipboard</guilabel>: if checked, &krusader; will place "
"search text to clipboard when a found file is opened."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Poizvedba v odložišče</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; bo "
"iskalno besedilo postavil v odložišče, ko se odpre najdena datoteka."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The above screen shot shows a search for all the files which end with "
"<literal role=\"extension\">c, cpp</literal> or <literal role=\"extension"
"\">h</literal> and include the string <literal>'testing 123'</literal>. "
"&krusader; will search in <filename class=\"directory\">/root, /opt, /bin</"
"filename> and <filename class=\"directory\">/usr</filename>, but not in "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/lib</filename> and <filename class="
"\"directory\">/usr/share</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Zgornji posnetek zaslona prikazuje iskanje vseh datotek, ki se končajo z "
"<literal role=\"extension\">c, cpp</literal> ali <literal role=\"extension"
"\">h</literal> in vključujejo niz <literal> 'testiranje 123'</literal>. "
"&krusader; bo iskal v <filename class=\"directory\">/root, /opt, /bin</"
"filename> in <filename class=\"directory\">/usr</filename>, ne pa v "
"<filename class=\"directory\"> /usr/lib</filename> in <filename class="
"\"directory\">/usr/share</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the <guibutton>Search</guibutton> button starts the search and "
"displays the results page. During the search, you may press the "
"<guibutton>Stop</guibutton> button to stop the search. The <guibutton>Close</"
"guibutton> button is not operational during a search, so you must first stop "
"the search and then <guibutton>Close</guibutton> the window. When a result "
"is found, double-clicking on it will take &krusader;'s active panel point to "
"the found files - but will not close the search window, so you will be able "
"to click on a different result."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Išči</guibutton> se začne iskanje in prikaže "
"stran z rezultati. Med iskanjem lahko pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Ustavi</"
"guibutton>, da ustavite iskanje. Gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton> med "
"iskanjem ne deluje, zato morate najprej ustaviti iskanje in nato "
"<guibutton>Zapreti</guibutton> okno. Ko je rezultat najden, bo dvojni klik "
"nanj usmeril aktivno ploščo &krusader; do najdenih datotek - vendar ne bo "
"zaprl iskalnega okna, tako da boste lahko kliknili drug rezultat."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes, you need to narrow your search even more. KruSearcher allows a "
"much finer search, and for that, let's look at the <guilabel>Advanced Page</"
"guilabel>..."
msgstr ""
"Včasih morate iskanje še bolj zožiti. KruSearcher omogoča veliko natančnejše "
"iskanje in za to poglejmo <guilabel>Napredno stran</guilabel>..."

#. Tag: title
#: search.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Advanced Search</title>"
msgstr "<title>Napredno iskanje</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: search.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Advanced Search</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Napredno iskanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This screen shot shows a search for files whose size is between 10KiB and "
"150KiB, which were modified between October 10th and November 1st, which "
"belong to any user in the 'nobody' group, and are readable and writable by "
"anyone in the 'nobody' group, but only readable to the rest of the world."
msgstr ""
"Ta posnetek zaslona prikazuje iskanje datotek, katerih velikost je med 10KiB "
"in 150KiB, ki so bile spremenjene med 10. oktobrom in 1. novembrom, ki "
"pripadajo kateremu koli uporabniku v skupini 'nihče' in jih lahko bere in "
"piše kdorkoli v skupini 'nihče'. skupino, vendar berljivo le preostalemu "
"svetu."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The advanced page is divided into three parts: size, date and ownership."
msgstr ""
"Napredna stran je razdeljena na tri dele: velikost, datum in lastništvo."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: search.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size"
msgstr "Velikost"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to choose the size range of the file you are looking for. By "
"checking the check boxes, you can search for a file which is bigger than XXX "
"bytes (or KB, MB), smaller than XXX bytes or, by checking both search for a "
"file which size is bigger than XXX but smaller than YYY."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam izbiro obsega velikosti datoteke, ki jo iščete. Če označite "
"potrditvena polja, lahko poiščete datoteko, ki je večja od XXX bajtov (ali "
"KB, MB), manjša od XXX bajtov ali, če označite oboje, poiščete datoteko, ki "
"je večja od XXX, vendar manjša od YYY."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: search.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Datum"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "This part offers three different ways of defining a date criteria:"
msgstr "Ta del ponuja tri različne načine definiranja merila datuma:"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Modified between</guilabel>: allows you to enter two dates. "
"&krusader; will search for files with a modification date between the first "
"date and the second one, inclusive."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Spremenjeno med</guilabel>: omogoča vnos dveh datumov. &krusader; "
"bo iskal datoteke z datumom spremembe med prvim in drugim datumom."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can click on the date icon (near the input boxes) to open a standard "
"date window - which allows you to easily browse through the calendar and "
"search for the desired date. Clicking on a date will close the window and "
"the date will appear in the input box."
msgstr ""
"Lahko kliknete ikono datuma (v bližini vnosnih polj), da odprete standardno "
"okno z datumom - ki vam omogoča preprosto brskanje po koledarju in iskanje "
"želenega datuma. S klikom na datum se okno zapre in datum se prikaže v "
"vnosnem polju."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Not modified after</guilabel>: choosing this option makes "
"&krusader; search for files that were NOT modified after a given date, which "
"is the same as searching for files older than that date."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ni spremenjeno po</guilabel>: če izberete to možnost, bo "
"&krusader; iskanje datotek, ki NISO bile spremenjene po določenem datumu, "
"kar je enako iskanju datotek, starejših od tega datuma."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Modified in the last/not modified in the last</guilabel>: in these "
"input boxes, you do not enter a date but a number. This number represents "
"days/weeks/months (as chosen in the near drop box). Entering the number 5 in "
"the upper input box, makes &krusader; search for files that were modified in "
"the last 5 days. Entering the number 2 in the lower input box makes "
"&krusader; search for files that did NOT change in the last 2 days. The "
"combination of both results in a search for files that were changed in the "
"last 5 days, but NOT in the last 2 days."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zadnje spremenjeno/nezadnje spremenjeno</guilabel>: v ta vnosna "
"polja ne vnašate datuma, temveč številko. Ta številka predstavlja dneve/"
"tedne/mesece (kot je izbrano v bližnjem spustnem polju). Če vnesete številko "
"5 v zgornje vnosno polje, bo &krusader; poiščite datoteke, ki so bile "
"spremenjene v zadnjih 5 dneh. Če v spodnje polje za vnos vnesete številko 2, "
"bo &krusader; poiščite datoteke, ki se NISO spremenile v zadnjih 2 dneh. "
"Kombinacija obeh povzroči iskanje datotek, ki so bile spremenjene v zadnjih "
"5 dneh, vendar NE v zadnjih 2 dneh."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: search.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ownership"
msgstr "Lastništvo"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Belongs to user/group</guilabel>: by checking each of the "
"corresponding check boxes, you can search for files which belong to a "
"certain user and/or group. The drop box lists all the user names and group "
"names in the system, just choose one and go ahead."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pripada uporabniku/skupini</guilabel>: če označite vsako od "
"ustreznih potrditvenih polj, lahko iščete datoteke, ki pripadajo določenemu "
"uporabniku in/ali skupini. V spustnem polju so navedena vsa uporabniška "
"imena in imena skupin v sistemu, samo izberite enega in nadaljujte."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Permissions</guilabel>: divided into owner, group and all - it "
"allows you to choose certain permissions for the file. You can choose to "
"specify permissions for the owner, group, all or any combination. The "
"question mark (?) is a wildcard - which means that any permission is valid."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dovoljenja</guilabel>: razdeljena na lastnika, skupino in vse - "
"omogoča vam izbiro določenih dovoljenj za datoteko. Izberete lahko "
"dovoljenja za lastnika, skupino, vse ali katero koli kombinacijo. Vprašaj "
"(?) je nadomestni znak - kar pomeni, da je vsako dovoljenje veljavno."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To clarify, the screen shot above (the ownership part) describes a search "
"for files that belong to any user in group 'users', are readable, writable "
"but not executable to any user in the group, are readable but not writable "
"or executable to the rest of the world and have unknown permissions to its "
"owner."
msgstr ""
"Za pojasnitev, zgornji posnetek zaslona (del o lastništvu) opisuje iskanje "
"datotek, ki pripadajo kateremu koli uporabniku v skupini 'uporabniki', so "
"berljive, zapisljive, vendar niso izvedljive za nobenega uporabnika v "
"skupini, so berljive, vendar ne zapisljive ali izvedljive za preostali svet "
"in imajo neznana dovoljenja za svojega lastnika."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: search.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Results"
msgstr "Rezultati"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the <guibutton>Search</guibutton> button to start the search and "
"open the Results window. Here you can see the progress and the results of "
"the search action. If you want you can stop the current search action with "
"the <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> button. In the result list select the file "
"and use <keycap>F3</keycap>/ <keycap>F4</keycap> to view/edit or use the "
"right-click menu. When you click on a found item, the folder of the active "
"panel will change if the selected item is not in the current panel folder. "
"The results window supports dragging items to other windows and copy to "
"clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>). "
"When you close the KruSearcher window, the selected item is selected in the "
"active panel."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na gumb <guibutton>Išči</guibutton>, da začnete iskanje in odprete "
"okno z rezultati. Tukaj si lahko ogledate napredek in rezultate iskalne "
"akcije. Če želite, lahko ustavite trenutno iskalno dejanje z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton>. Na seznamu rezultatov izberite datoteko in "
"uporabite <keycap>F3</keycap>/ <keycap>F4</keycap> za ogled/urejanje ali "
"uporabite meni z desnim klikom. Ko kliknete na najden element, se bo mapa "
"aktivne plošče spremenila, če izbrani element ni v trenutni mapi plošče. "
"Okno z rezultati podpira vlečenje elementov v druga okna in kopiranje v "
"odložišče (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>). "
"Ko zaprete okno KruSearcher, je izbrani element izbran na aktivni plošči."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: search.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Feed to listbox"
msgstr "Prenesi v seznamsko polje"

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the <guibutton>Feed to listbox</guibutton> button after the "
"results are displayed, then &krusader; ask for a Query Name, this name will "
"be used in the Results-Tab in the List Panel that holds the search results. "
"You can do whatever you want on the files in the new tab. The location "
"toolbar will display &eg; <filename>virt:/Search results 1</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Ko po prikazu rezultatov kliknete gumb <guibutton>Prenesi v seznam</"
"guibutton>, &krusader; prosite za ime poizvedbe, bo to ime uporabljeno na "
"zavihku Rezultati na plošči seznama, ki vsebuje rezultate iskanja. Z "
"datotekami v novem zavihku lahko počnete, kar želite. Orodna vrstica "
"lokacije bo prikazala &eg; <filename>virt:/Rezultati iskanja 1</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: search.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The files in the Results-Tab are actually the original files. if you delete "
"a file - it is removed!"
msgstr ""
"Datoteke na zavihku z rezultati so pravzaprav izvirne datoteke. če izbrišete "
"datoteko - je odstranjena!"
